All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisConfig
    The AnalysisConfig class is used to configure the api key of IBM Personality Insights Service.
    AnalysisController
    The AnalysisConctroller is used to handle analysis related requests.
    AnalysisResult
    The AnalysisResult is used to store the related data for analysis.
    Application
    This Application class is the starter of the SpringBoot.
    AuthConfig
    The AuthConfig class is used to configure the consumer key for Twitter API.
    AuthController
    The AuthController class is used to handle the authorization related requests.
    BasicCharacter
    The BasicCharacter class represents the character of the game, and it contains the id and the name of the player, and the basic attributes.
    BattleController
    The BattleController class is used to handle the battle related requests
    BattleService
    The BattleService class is used to handle the result of battle
    Bot
    The Bot class represents the bot character of the game It extends the BasicCharacter class.
    Ideal
    The Ideal class represents the ideal personality of the player.
    IdealController
    The IdealController class is used to handle the ideal related requests.
    IdealRepository
    The repository of Ideal which extends JpaRepository.
    IdealService
    The IdealService interface defines the operations on Ideal in the database
    IdealServiceImpl
    Implementation of IdealService
    PageErrorController
    The PageErrorController is used to handle error page.
    PersonalityInsightService
    The PersonalityInsightService provide the analysis of tweets based on IBM Personality Insights API
    Player
    The Player class represents the real character of the player.
    PlayerConfig
    The PlayerConfig class is used to configure the experience and attributes of players for each level.
    PlayerController
    The PlayerController class is used to handle the player related requests.
    PlayerRepository
    The repository of Player which extends JpaRepository.
    PlayerService
    The PlayerService interface defines the operations on Player in the database
    PlayerServiceImpl
    Implementation of PlayerService
    RedisConfig
    This RedisConfig class is used to configure the Redis.
    RedisService
    The RedisService provides the temporary cache of data
    TwitterService
    The TwitterService provide authorization of Twitter and access of tweets
    User
    The User class represents the account of the user.
    UserController
    The UserController class is used to handle the user related requests.
    UserRepository
    The repository of User which extends JpaRepository.
    UserService
    The UserService interface defines the operations on User in the database
    UserServiceImpl
    Implementation of UserService
